# Rule: Tailwind-only cursor

- **ID:** react19-tailwind-cursor
- **Scope:** src/**/*.tsx, src/**/*.jsx
- **Description:**  
  Enforce that all cursor styles use Tailwind utility classes (`cursor-pointer`, `cursor-wait`, etc.).
  ❌ No inline `style={{ cursor: ... }}`  
  ❌ No raw CSS `cursor:` declarations  
  ✅ Always prefer Tailwind `cursor-*` utilities.

## Checks

### ❌ Inline style
- Pattern: `style={{*cursor*}}`
- Message: "Do not use inline cursor styles. Use Tailwind cursor-* utilities instead."
- Severity: error

### ❌ Raw CSS
- Pattern: `cursor:`
- Where: `*.css`
- Message: "Do not set cursor in raw CSS. Use Tailwind cursor-* utilities instead."
- Severity: error

### ✅ Encourage Tailwind
- Pattern: `className=*`
- Message: "Use Tailwind cursor-* utilities (e.g. cursor-pointer, cursor-grab)."
- Severity: info

